public abstract static sealed class RegistryServices.BaseRegistry extends Object implements ITypeInferencing<Collection<Class<? extends RegistryServices.RegistryEntry>>> permits RegistryServices.EphemeralRegistry, RegistryServices.WeakRegistry, RegistryServices.ExternRegistry
This is the root class used by all of the various implementations of a Registry. Registries are meant to be collatable groups of properties.
